{"type":"article_comment","id":488181,"parentType":"article","parentId":23649,"uid":34697,"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JpEY3LW.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JpEY3LW.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JpEY3LW.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n我觉得某些问题可以修改一下：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RMHzGPh.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RMHzGPh.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RMHzGPh.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n这个应该说清楚是具体侵犯的是什么利益。如果是侵犯法定最低工资，最高工时，同工同资这样的权利的话那我同意，如果是违反契约，单方面扣工资这样的事情那我反对。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EuvgA8b.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EuvgA8b.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EuvgA8b.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n我想私有化学校，然后让不同的学校选择他们自己想教的价值观，然后由家长和学生来选他们想去的学校。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Lg5dpU3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Lg5dpU3.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Lg5dpU3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n根本问题不是懒惰，而是违约（当然如果契约里有写的话那随意）。而且如果霸占工厂不让其他人应聘的话，那也是侵犯他人权利。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gUG2WMb.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gUG2WMb.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gUG2WMb.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n中国是啥？我如果想分裂呢？<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/OYGMber.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OYGMber.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/OYGMber.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n我想把教育，医疗，住房全部私有化。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1UCYXgm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1UCYXgm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1UCYXgm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n我想让各个农产品公司决定他们想怎么生产。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/W30u5B2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W30u5B2.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/W30u5B2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n我想让各个私立慈善基金、孤儿院决定他们要怎么选择收养父母。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qIkOitZ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qIkOitZ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qIkOitZ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n如果指定了完善的私有产权法律的话，这不会是一个问题。","date":"2020-09-04","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}